NEW ZEALAND: Vice-chancellors=92 body changes name=20

John Gerritsen
The New Zealand Vice-Chancellors Committee changed its name last week,
saying that more than ever before it needed to speak with a unified voice.
Full report on the University World News site:
http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?story=3D2010080617481117

