---------------------------------------------------------------------------

INDIA: Foreign providers: putting national needs first

Rahul Choudaha and Alan Ruby*
As the bill to open up India=92s higher education sector to foreign
providers wends its way through the legislative process, the government
needs to consider what is best for the country. Not everyone needs an MBA
from Mumbai or Delhi.
Full report on the University World News site:
http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?story=3D2010080617332087
